{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_15_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 2話 好きに、なってきちゃった",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ライブに向けてみんな練習を頑張っているみたいだな\nおーい、差し入れのドリンクを持って来――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "そこで止まって下さい、{user}さん\nはい、動かないで。両手は上に！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.7558958371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "れ、怜？　それに古手川さんも……今度はなんだ？\n俺はただ差し入れを持って来ただけだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6333334287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そのドリンク……\n飲んだら何か、良からぬことになったりしませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.118458112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "モモの宇宙植物の中には、花粉や匂いに\n様々な効果を持つものもあるみたいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4517914454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "何かの拍子に\nそのドリンクに混ざってしまっているかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.718458112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "これはそこのコーヒーショップのだぞ？\nさすがに疑い過ぎじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "何が起きるか分からない以上\n警戒するに越したことはありません。例えば――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4010204632,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drink-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12533.333333400002,
          "startTime": 60.9343537966
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "差し入れのドリンク、ありがとうございます\nそれでは、いただきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4010204632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　なんだか体が熱くなってきて……\n{user}さんが意外と格好良く見える……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.567685604,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 16753.32977289999,
          "startTime": 86.3210153769
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "好きに、なってきちゃったかも……ううん、好き！\n世界一好き、大好きです！　ぎゅ～～っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0010153769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "――みたいなことが起きるかもしれません！\n急に相手を好きになるだなんて……ハレンチだわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4676820436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "想像が飛躍し過ぎてないか！？\nだが、最近のトラブルを考えると、ありえるのか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3666626931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "そういう訳ですから！\n飲み物が安全かどうかチェックさせて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.8197191555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "別に構わないが、どうやって確認するんだ？\n検査器具なんてどこにもないだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.8065574151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "まず{user}さんが飲んで\nその次に私達が飲むというのはどうでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2429165521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "数人でチェックすれば安全度は高まります\nコップを用意するのでどうぞ一口飲んで下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2503407093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（まさか怜がここまで暴走してしまうとは……）\n（ライブに影響が出なければいいんだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.9999960264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマスライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2984134038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.4317462285
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.4984205246
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "唯の協力のおかげで、今日のライブを\n無事に迎えることが出来たけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.1741278329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "もしかしたら、ライブ中も何かが\n起きてしまうかもしれない……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.6741278329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.7598268349
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（ん？　舞台袖にいるのは……怜か？）\n（不安そうな表情でどうしたんだ？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.9142485458
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ、本番だからこそ警戒しなくっちゃ\n例えば、ステージの上で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.4139476398,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3552.477635799988,
          "startTime": 162.9664252756
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 18537.16043419999,
          "startTime": 177.951108074
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasstage-00-night",
      "startTime": 162.7164252756
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasstage-00-night",
      "startTime": 162.7164252756
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "みんなー！　今日は来てくれてありが……\nえ？　な、何あれ……掃除機？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.3844454763,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cleaner-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3418.0161317,
          "startTime": 167.1844414073
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cleaner-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8133.3333333000155,
          "startTime": 176.5177788096
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasstage-00-night",
      "startTime": 173.4599850493
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasstage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasstage-00-night",
      "startTime": 176.5177788096
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、ララの発明品が暴走してるの！？\nちょっ……きゃ～！　ふ、服が吸い込まれる～！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.5177788096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 182.9833270548
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 182.9833270548
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "……みたいなことが起きるかもしれないわ！\nもっと酷いことになるかも……ど、どうしよう！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.851112143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 191.9819211799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_02-koh008.m4a",
